WEBVTT

00:05.471 --> 00:07.139
(THUNDER BOOMING)

00:22.088 --> 00:23.422
(SCREAMING)

00:39.773 --> 00:41.440
(SNORING)

00:41.442 --> 00:43.275
(BLOB SPEAKING BLOBBISH)

00:43.277 --> 00:48.113
But Dad, I'm not too small
to have big ideas!

00:49.482 --> 00:51.917
(SPEAKING BLOBBISH)

00:51.919 --> 00:53.218
(BELL RINGING)

00:53.220 --> 00:55.354
(SPEAKING BLOBBISH)

00:55.356 --> 00:57.322
Ugh! Who?
What? Where?

00:57.324 --> 00:58.424
Oh, hi!

00:58.426 --> 01:00.559
Welcome to Spa Transyl...

01:00.561 --> 01:02.261
(YAWNING)
...vania!

01:02.263 --> 01:04.730
A place so relaxing, um, ah,

01:04.732 --> 01:07.232
even the employees
fall asleep!

01:07.234 --> 01:09.701
Ha! Some employees.

01:11.004 --> 01:11.437
Hi, Mavis!

01:11.439 --> 01:13.672
I thought you were working
in the gift shop?

01:13.674 --> 01:16.642
I am. I mean... I was.

01:16.644 --> 01:20.846
Why is all this cool stuff
so out of reach?

01:23.183 --> 01:26.151
Mavis, you sly bat.

01:26.153 --> 01:28.287
(BARKING)

01:29.522 --> 01:31.390
(GLASS BREAKING)

01:33.760 --> 01:36.295
I also did some time
in room service.

01:36.297 --> 01:38.330
<i>Wasn't to my taste.</i>

01:38.332 --> 01:40.065
Room service!

01:40.300 --> 01:42.134
Voila!
Eggs three ways!

01:42.136 --> 01:43.969
(CLUCKING IN HORROR)

01:45.705 --> 01:49.575
Oops! Room 999.
That's on me!

01:49.577 --> 01:50.943
And now, I'm here!

01:50.945 --> 01:53.612
(GASPING)
You subscribe to <i>Brew-haha,</i>

01:53.614 --> 01:55.414
the magazine
for Witch Humor?

01:55.416 --> 01:57.850
My dad says I'm
too little for that.

01:57.852 --> 01:58.617
No way!

01:58.619 --> 01:59.985
Knock-knock.
Who's there?

01:59.987 --> 02:00.752
Witch.
Witch who?

02:00.754 --> 02:03.355
Witch spa product
are you gonna try first?

02:03.357 --> 02:05.491
"Drac don't Crack."

02:05.725 --> 02:07.059
MAVIS: Drac don't Crack!

02:07.061 --> 02:12.197
I'm 114, but I don't look
a day over 85!

02:12.199 --> 02:14.700
Oh, brother.

02:14.702 --> 02:18.403
"99.9% blob?"
You make this, Daddy?

02:18.405 --> 02:19.438
(SPEAKING BLOBBISH)

02:19.440 --> 02:22.374
Aw, I wish you'd let me make
some of my ideas.

02:22.376 --> 02:24.676
Blob Water, for when
you feel like something

02:24.678 --> 02:27.479
in-between water and ice.

02:27.881 --> 02:30.315
(SPEAKING BLOBBISH)

02:30.984 --> 02:32.251
It's so unfair!

02:32.253 --> 02:34.319
I'm tired of having
my ideas ignored

02:34.321 --> 02:36.889
and being told I'm
too small and cute.

02:36.891 --> 02:38.557
(GROWLING AND BARKING)

02:38.559 --> 02:41.293
Aw, adorbs.

02:41.628 --> 02:42.227
Sorry.

02:42.229 --> 02:44.930
Y'know, smallness
can be a plus.

02:44.932 --> 02:46.265
I mean,
you're the hero

02:46.267 --> 02:48.000
whose tiny arm
unlocks the door

02:48.002 --> 02:49.868
when your dad
forgets his key.

02:49.870 --> 02:51.937
I wish he'd
see it that way.

02:51.939 --> 02:54.139
Stop wishing
and start doing!

02:54.141 --> 02:55.340
Like me.
My dad never said...

02:55.342 --> 02:59.678
(MIMICS DRACULA)
"Mavis, make the hotel
better," I just did!

03:00.914 --> 03:03.115
Ooh! For me?

03:03.216 --> 03:04.616
My dearest, Mavy Wavy.

03:04.618 --> 03:09.388
I've been hearing a lot
about your "helping out"
at the hotel.

03:09.390 --> 03:12.457
Maybe cool it on
that front for a while.

03:12.459 --> 03:13.725
Love, Dad.

03:13.727 --> 03:14.593
(GROWLING)

03:14.595 --> 03:15.661
Wendy, it's time
to show my...

03:15.663 --> 03:19.998
Uh, your dad just what I...
Uh, we... Uh, you can do!

03:22.001 --> 03:24.536
Mr. Blob,
you look stressed.

03:24.538 --> 03:27.639
Let Hotel "Transylvaniahh"
help you.

03:27.641 --> 03:30.809
Relaxation is
our specialty!

03:31.044 --> 03:33.312
(GRUNTING AND YELPING)

03:35.815 --> 03:37.249
Follow me!

03:38.918 --> 03:42.754
This sauna gives heat
that can't be beat!

03:44.691 --> 03:45.457
(INHALES DEEPLY)

03:45.459 --> 03:48.493
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
Easy pard'ner.

03:48.495 --> 03:52.731
You're not ready for
sauna duty just yet.

03:52.733 --> 03:55.767
Watch and burn.

03:56.536 --> 03:58.103
(BLOWING)

03:58.105 --> 04:01.840
Now for Operation:
Show Our Dads
They're Wrong!

04:01.842 --> 04:04.276
Code name: Gum Drop!

04:04.444 --> 04:06.478
We can work on names
on the way.

04:06.480 --> 04:08.614
To the Blob Factory!

04:08.616 --> 04:10.515
(LAUGHING GIDDILY)

04:19.858 --> 04:21.125
(BEEPS)

04:24.964 --> 04:27.799
WENDY: This is where
the magic happens.

04:27.801 --> 04:32.804
Blobburger in a can,
blob on the cob,
Easter Blobbys.

04:32.939 --> 04:35.307
So, what does
your dad do all day?

04:35.309 --> 04:39.911
He pretty much just hooks
himself up to the extractor
and spews blob.

04:39.913 --> 04:40.379
That's it!

04:40.381 --> 04:43.081
What? What?
Something caught in my jelly?

04:43.083 --> 04:46.418
To the Blob Extractor!
What?

04:47.487 --> 04:48.754
(POWERING DOWN)

04:48.756 --> 04:51.590
Time to show
our dads who's boss!

04:51.592 --> 04:54.993
In there?
No, no way. No, no.

04:54.995 --> 04:55.961
No, I'm not ready.

04:55.963 --> 04:58.063
Hmm, when you say
"I'm not ready,"

04:58.065 --> 05:01.500
all I hear is...
(SPEAKING BLOBBISH)

05:01.601 --> 05:03.502
"You're a purple
pickle butt?"

05:03.504 --> 05:06.071
My Blobbish is
a little rusty.

05:06.073 --> 05:07.806
Now, get in!

05:07.808 --> 05:09.574
Um, I don't know, Mavis.

05:09.576 --> 05:12.544
Wendy, this is your chance!

05:13.746 --> 05:14.980
Right.

05:19.886 --> 05:23.088
Whoo! He-he! I'm doing it!

05:23.090 --> 05:25.891
If we're gonna prove you can
handle more responsibility,

05:25.893 --> 05:28.126
we'll have to move
faster than this.

05:28.128 --> 05:30.062
Is there a turbo button?

05:30.064 --> 05:32.297
I dunno.
Check the manual.

05:33.533 --> 05:34.866
It's in Blobbish.

05:34.868 --> 05:36.902
And if I know
my Blobbish...

05:36.904 --> 05:37.803
Which you don't.

05:37.805 --> 05:39.838
I think...
(SPEAKING BLOBBISH)

05:39.840 --> 05:43.342
Means "pull this
large, obvious lever."

05:43.876 --> 05:45.610
(STRAINING)

05:45.612 --> 05:47.412
(ALARM SOUNDING)

05:49.882 --> 05:50.682
Uh-oh.

05:50.684 --> 05:53.585
What?
I said "uh-oh!"

05:53.587 --> 05:55.087
"Uh-oh?"

05:55.089 --> 05:57.155
Oh! Uh-oh.

05:59.192 --> 06:00.826
Whoa, the good news is

06:00.828 --> 06:04.062
your dad's not gonna
think you're too small.

06:04.064 --> 06:05.964
Holy rabies!

06:06.933 --> 06:10.469
What took you so long?
I said it was an emergency.

06:10.471 --> 06:14.172
Uh, that's why we stopped
for emergency tacos.

06:14.174 --> 06:15.374
(BUZZING)

06:15.376 --> 06:19.811
And then
when you said it was
a really big emergency,

06:19.813 --> 06:22.647
we had to go back
and get 'em supersized.

06:22.649 --> 06:23.682
(RUMBLING)

06:23.684 --> 06:26.985
Whoo! Whoopie! Ha-ha!

06:27.487 --> 06:31.123
HANK: Whoa!
Wendy got super-sized.

06:31.125 --> 06:34.793
Wow! I can see the hotel
from up here.

06:34.795 --> 06:36.762
And Hank's bald spot!

06:36.764 --> 06:38.663
It's a new scalp, okay?

06:38.665 --> 06:41.133
Just, uh,
stay right there.

06:41.135 --> 06:42.300
Don't make any
sudden movements

06:42.302 --> 06:44.736
until I figure out how
to make you small again.

06:44.738 --> 06:48.306
No way! I've been shrunken
down my whole life.

06:48.308 --> 06:50.442
Now's my chance to be big,

06:50.444 --> 06:52.577
big, big!

06:53.112 --> 06:54.546
So cool!

06:54.747 --> 06:55.547
Less cool!

06:55.549 --> 06:59.050
That so counts as
a "sudden movement!"

06:59.052 --> 07:00.252
Whoa! Whoo!

07:00.254 --> 07:03.422
I always wanted
a polka-dot carpet!

07:03.424 --> 07:05.590
(BOTH GASPING)

07:05.592 --> 07:09.361
Oh, no! My baby's
stuck in a well.

07:11.464 --> 07:14.166
Oh, no! My baby's
stuck in that blob!

07:14.168 --> 07:19.070
Don't worry!
We'll have your baby back
in that well in no time!

07:20.039 --> 07:23.141
I'm not too small
for this ride!

07:23.576 --> 07:24.643
(LOWING)

07:24.645 --> 07:26.611
We have to find a way
to stop her

07:26.613 --> 07:28.747
before someone else does!

07:28.881 --> 07:30.982
Who and which army?

07:30.984 --> 07:34.252
Code Blob! Code Blob!
(ALARM SOUNDING)

07:36.689 --> 07:39.291
Uh, that witch army!

07:40.626 --> 07:42.694
Er, roger, Witch Squadron!

07:42.696 --> 07:45.230
Release Shrink-O-Sprinkle
at will!

07:46.599 --> 07:49.367
(GIGGLING)
Stop!

07:49.369 --> 07:50.368
It's so tickly!

07:50.370 --> 07:53.038
This blob is just
too big to shrink!

07:53.040 --> 07:56.241
Return to base
for reinforcements!

07:58.878 --> 08:00.679
(GASPING)

08:01.214 --> 08:02.481
(LAUGHING)

08:02.483 --> 08:07.419
Wendy, you need to
get small again, like now,

08:07.421 --> 08:08.720
before you hurt somebody.

08:08.722 --> 08:13.124
No way, I just started to
get down with my big self.

08:13.126 --> 08:15.360
Check out the crew
I roll with.

08:15.362 --> 08:18.263
Besides, my dad hasn't
seen me yet!

08:18.265 --> 08:20.999
(GASPING) Your dad!

08:21.001 --> 08:24.135
Hank, you're in charge.
Do not let Wendy leave.

08:24.137 --> 08:29.007
Does it look like
I have any control
over this situation?

08:29.275 --> 08:32.943
Huh, why is
the door locked?
Where'd he go?

08:32.946 --> 08:34.980
(GASPING)
There he is!

08:34.982 --> 08:35.847
Holy rabies!

08:35.849 --> 08:38.049
The heat from
the sauna shrunk him,

08:38.051 --> 08:39.583
and it's all my fault!

08:39.586 --> 08:41.285
(HIGH-PITCHED BLOBBISH SOUNDS)

08:41.288 --> 08:44.589
And he's..
Thirsty for ketchup?

08:44.591 --> 08:47.492
Girl, you cannot
speak Blobbish.

08:47.494 --> 08:48.527
(SIGHING)

08:48.529 --> 08:51.530
He does look pretty
relaxed though.

08:51.764 --> 08:53.965
It's... It's jammed!

08:54.734 --> 08:56.768
With a zombie finger?

08:56.770 --> 08:58.036
(STRAINING)

08:58.038 --> 09:00.372
Let me try!
(STRAINING)

09:00.374 --> 09:03.775
And our hands are
too big to get it out!

09:03.777 --> 09:05.610
That's it! Too big!

09:05.612 --> 09:08.446
Sauna! Shrink!
Small! Mr. Blob...

09:08.448 --> 09:09.714
Tennis! Armpit!
Fire Ants!

09:09.716 --> 09:13.985
Oh, I thought we were
doing a shouting out
random words thing.

09:13.987 --> 09:17.556
Ugh! No! We're doing
a shrinking thing!

09:18.224 --> 09:22.394
Mr. Hydraberg!
And, uh, other Mr. Hydrabergs,

09:22.396 --> 09:24.062
I need your help.

09:31.337 --> 09:33.905
Ooh, a party hat!

09:33.907 --> 09:35.607
Whee! (LAUGHING)

09:35.609 --> 09:36.908
MAVIS: Wendy!

09:36.910 --> 09:37.909
Oh, hi, Mavis!

09:37.911 --> 09:41.279
Your Dad is in trouble
and needs your help.

09:41.281 --> 09:42.981
What? Oh, no!

09:42.983 --> 09:45.684
Wait, he needs my help?

09:45.686 --> 09:47.319
He must've heard
that I'm big now!

09:47.321 --> 09:50.689
Oh, no, no, no, no,
he needs your
small-Wendy help!

09:50.691 --> 09:53.625
We need your
tiny blobby hands
to unlock the sauna.

09:53.627 --> 09:56.394
This is your big...
Uh, little chance!

09:56.396 --> 09:57.295
Okay, I'm in!

09:57.297 --> 10:00.498
Uh... How am I gonna
get small again?

10:00.500 --> 10:01.900
No prob.

10:01.902 --> 10:03.702
(WHISTLING)

10:04.303 --> 10:06.938
Go ahead, kid.
You're ready.

10:06.940 --> 10:08.907
Oh, boy! Really?

10:08.909 --> 10:10.675
Yes, really!

10:19.518 --> 10:22.020
Stop! It's so tickley!

10:23.556 --> 10:25.590
Boom drac-a-lacka!

10:26.826 --> 10:30.228
WITCH:
Situation now under
control, squadron!

10:30.230 --> 10:31.863
(MOOING)

10:31.865 --> 10:33.665
My baby!

10:33.799 --> 10:36.901
Wendy, you're back!

10:37.803 --> 10:38.770
How does it feel?

10:38.772 --> 10:40.438
Between you and me,
exactly the same.

10:40.440 --> 10:43.808
But in a good way!
Let's go rescue my dad!

10:43.810 --> 10:46.444
To the spa!

10:51.884 --> 10:54.386
Yes!
You did it, Wendy!

10:54.388 --> 10:57.188
Daddy! I'm here
to save you!

10:57.490 --> 10:58.256
Daddy?

10:58.258 --> 11:00.925
(High-pitched Blobbish sounds)

11:00.927 --> 11:02.894
Oh! You're so tiny!

11:02.896 --> 11:06.364
Don't worry,
I won't hold it against you.

11:06.366 --> 11:07.465
I know how it feels.

11:07.467 --> 11:10.802
Now that I have
your attention,
let's talk Blob Water.

11:10.804 --> 11:13.571
Blob Water,
for when you don't want ice

11:13.573 --> 11:15.774
and you don't want water.

11:15.776 --> 11:18.910
You want something
in-between.

11:21.914 --> 11:24.382
(ORGAN PLAYING)

11:26.585 --> 11:29.721
<i>♪ Slug guts in my hair</i>

11:29.723 --> 11:32.023
<i>♪ Slug guts everywhere</i>

11:32.025 --> 11:35.627
<i>♪ And I don't really care!</i>

11:35.629 --> 11:37.062
(SQUEALING HAPPILY)
Mavis!

11:37.064 --> 11:40.532
Can you believe Jett Black
is coming here today?

11:40.534 --> 11:46.037
Is that today? Huh.
Must've slipped my mind.

11:46.972 --> 11:48.406
(SIGHING)

11:48.408 --> 11:49.841
(LAUGHING)

11:49.843 --> 11:52.343
Come on, you think
I'm gonna get all blubbery

11:52.345 --> 11:54.646
over some teen rock god?

11:54.648 --> 11:55.580
(FEEDBACK)

11:55.582 --> 11:58.416
(LOUD SOLO PLAYING)

12:01.020 --> 12:02.954
(SQUEALING HAPPILY)

12:03.923 --> 12:08.126
Sorry, think your jaw came
unhinged there for a sec.

12:08.128 --> 12:09.327
Hey, I'm...

12:09.329 --> 12:10.528
Ridiculous gor-mous!

12:10.530 --> 12:13.631
I mean, what I'm trying
to say is hi, I'm Hotel.

12:13.633 --> 12:16.501
Welcome to
Mavis Transylspatula!

12:16.503 --> 12:17.702
Smooth.

12:17.704 --> 12:21.773
You've got a little,
ya know, something...

12:22.508 --> 12:23.575
Yeah.

12:23.577 --> 12:26.244
(GASPING AND SCREAMING)

12:27.613 --> 12:29.247
Ugh, what a fan girl.

12:29.249 --> 12:33.885
I mean, as if we'd go
all fan boy over phlegm
ball superstar...

12:33.887 --> 12:36.821
(GASPING)
Noosh La Loosh!

12:37.590 --> 12:42.293
Sign my face! No! No!
Sign his leg!

12:43.696 --> 12:45.897
It's the Nooshster!

12:46.499 --> 12:47.565
(GROANING)

12:47.567 --> 12:51.636
I can't believe how bad
I blew it with Jett.

12:51.638 --> 12:54.339
So, you didn't
give him your song?

12:54.341 --> 12:56.908
No, I didn't give him my song.

12:56.910 --> 12:57.909
I had a whole plan, too.

12:57.911 --> 13:02.814
He'd read it, love it,
beg me to record it,
and boom drac-alacka,

13:02.816 --> 13:04.449
number one hit!

13:04.451 --> 13:05.884
It would have been so easy.

13:05.886 --> 13:09.654
It was gonna be!
Until the spider in my teeth.

13:09.656 --> 13:13.691
How's Jett gonna take me
seriously after that?

13:13.693 --> 13:19.164
You don't know how
lucky you are to have
a reflection, Wendy.

13:19.166 --> 13:20.265
Blob freeze?

13:20.267 --> 13:20.932
(SQUEALING)

13:20.934 --> 13:27.338
Very good, <i>Monsieur</i> Black!
Your room service will
arrive in 15 minutes!

13:27.340 --> 13:29.808
Or whenever it is ready!

13:29.810 --> 13:34.145
Hmm, that gives me an idea.

13:35.581 --> 13:38.483
Okay, 15 minutes to
intercept Jett's order,

13:38.485 --> 13:42.253
and get a second chance
at a first impression!

13:43.289 --> 13:46.024
Razor sharp
widow's peak, check!

13:46.026 --> 13:49.861
Dazzling white fangs, check!

13:50.162 --> 13:51.496
Blood drained cheeks for that

13:51.498 --> 13:53.731
ghostly pale complexion,
check!

13:53.733 --> 13:55.266
(GASPING) Holy rabies!

13:55.268 --> 13:56.134
I'm late!

13:56.136 --> 13:59.103
Jett's next hit song, check!

14:00.105 --> 14:02.574
(SYNTHESIZER PLAYING)

14:02.576 --> 14:05.109
(SYNTHESIZER PLAYING)

14:05.111 --> 14:06.644
(KNOCKING)

14:07.546 --> 14:10.548
Oh, hey.
Spider fangs, right.

14:10.550 --> 14:11.549
(LAUGHS) Yeah!

14:11.551 --> 14:15.920
See I was kinda
nervous to meet you,
'cause I wrote this song.

14:15.922 --> 14:17.822
Here, check it out!

14:17.957 --> 14:18.990
I'm gonna stop you
right there.

14:18.992 --> 14:23.761
But, you know, you've got
something on your face.

14:23.763 --> 14:25.563
(GASPING)
Yeah.

14:25.565 --> 14:27.332
(SCREAMING)

14:27.334 --> 14:30.068
Ooh, spoiled kumquats, lovely.

14:30.070 --> 14:31.703
Take that, punk!

14:31.705 --> 14:32.537
(GROANING ANGRILY)

14:32.539 --> 14:36.808
Sometimes being
a vampire stinks!

14:37.810 --> 14:40.879
Mavis! What's the occasion?

14:40.881 --> 14:45.083
You look positively...
Ah, c'mon, ref!

14:45.085 --> 14:45.884
Ghastly!

14:45.886 --> 14:48.786
It'd be nice
to see for myself!

14:48.788 --> 14:52.056
Yeah. Sometimes
I pee myself too.

14:52.058 --> 14:53.458
(SCREAMING)
Uncle Gene,

14:53.460 --> 14:57.462
why isn't there a mirror
for vampires?

14:57.464 --> 15:00.365
(CHUCKLING)
But there is, sweetie.

15:00.367 --> 15:01.900
The Dark Glass.

15:01.902 --> 15:04.369
Dungeon 665B.

15:04.371 --> 15:06.604
Bicycle kick, sucka!

15:06.606 --> 15:09.707
What? Why'd no one
ever tell me?

15:11.343 --> 15:13.211
Thanks, Uncle Gene!

15:13.213 --> 15:14.679
Boom drac-a-lacka!

15:14.681 --> 15:18.683
But I wouldn't go
down there if I were you.

15:18.685 --> 15:22.320
The Dark Glass is
super cursed and...

15:22.322 --> 15:24.422
Goal!

15:27.192 --> 15:28.359
Whoa.

15:28.361 --> 15:29.961
It's real?

15:30.262 --> 15:31.896
(GASPING)

15:31.898 --> 15:33.197
Ah!

15:34.333 --> 15:35.633
Yes!

15:35.901 --> 15:38.803
So that's what I look like!

15:38.805 --> 15:40.405
(LAUGHING)

15:40.407 --> 15:43.541
This is incredible!

15:43.543 --> 15:45.276
Oh, hey. Oh nice fangs.

15:45.278 --> 15:47.078
Uh-huh. Oh, hey Jett.

15:47.080 --> 15:48.947
Yeah, I'm Mavis.
What's that?

15:48.949 --> 15:50.949
You... You want me
to hear my song?

15:50.951 --> 15:54.052
Oh, I don't know,
I... Okay!

15:54.054 --> 15:56.287
This is so awesome.

15:56.289 --> 15:58.589
I gotta show somebody!

16:00.292 --> 16:01.826
(GROANING)

16:04.997 --> 16:07.598
Hey, hey,
he's gonna do it!

16:09.034 --> 16:10.468
(GROWLING)

16:10.470 --> 16:14.038
It's funny, I know
how it's gonna end
every time,

16:14.040 --> 16:16.174
but I still can't help
but watch.

16:16.176 --> 16:17.008
Hmm, me too.
(GROANING)

16:17.010 --> 16:21.346
Looks like Mavis is
gonna try and bomb
with Jett again.

16:21.348 --> 16:23.581
She really is a glutton
for punishment.

16:23.583 --> 16:25.516
(GROANING)

16:26.385 --> 16:29.320
Oh, hey, listen,
I don't really... Ah!

16:29.322 --> 16:31.456
Ow! No. No, wait!

16:31.458 --> 16:35.626
She just knocked me over
like I didn't even exist.

16:35.628 --> 16:37.395
How cool!

16:37.397 --> 16:39.263
(GROANING)

16:39.798 --> 16:41.366
Uh, did you see that?

16:41.368 --> 16:44.035
Wow. The pressure of
hanging around a celeb

16:44.037 --> 16:45.303
is really gettin' to her.

16:45.305 --> 16:48.506
We could probably
teach her a thing
or two about...

16:48.508 --> 16:50.241
(GASPS)
Noosh!

16:52.011 --> 16:53.344
Silly boys.

16:53.346 --> 16:57.348
It's not like Blobbio
walked in and...

16:57.816 --> 17:00.818
(SHRIEKING)

17:01.353 --> 17:05.022
You guys are
not gonna believe
what just happened!

17:05.025 --> 17:07.959
I saw myself. As in me!

17:07.961 --> 17:09.060
In a mirror!

17:09.061 --> 17:13.364
Did you hear me?
A mirror! For vampires!

17:13.732 --> 17:14.832
Seriously?

17:14.834 --> 17:17.367
You've got nothing to say?

17:18.237 --> 17:19.637
(BLOWING RASPBERRY)

17:19.638 --> 17:22.839
(GASPS)
Guys, guys!

17:22.842 --> 17:24.208
Wait!

17:24.210 --> 17:27.178
Uh, what was that all about?

17:27.479 --> 17:31.015
Ugh, this is
so not my day.

17:31.017 --> 17:33.017
It's like everyone's
gone crazy

17:33.019 --> 17:35.720
since I looked
in that dumb mirror.

17:35.722 --> 17:37.522
You looked at it?

17:37.524 --> 17:42.093
Why would you do that?
I told you it was cursed!

17:42.095 --> 17:44.462
Cursed?
You didn't say that!

17:44.464 --> 17:46.531
If a vampire looks
at the Dark Glass,

17:46.533 --> 17:51.169
their reflection comes to life
as a hollow, mindless clone!

17:51.171 --> 17:52.703
Everybody knows that.

17:52.705 --> 17:56.841
So, right now,
there's another Mavis
walking around,

17:56.843 --> 17:59.277
freaking everybody out?
I gotta stop her!

17:59.279 --> 18:02.647
I wouldn't do that
if I were you!

18:03.048 --> 18:05.216
And she's gone. Okay.

18:05.218 --> 18:08.853
Now, if I was me,
where would I be?

18:08.855 --> 18:10.755
(ALL LAUGHING)

18:10.757 --> 18:12.123
(GROANING)

18:12.125 --> 18:14.826
Ugh. How embarrassing.

18:14.828 --> 18:18.996
Come on! We gotta
get you outta here!

18:19.398 --> 18:20.731
Ow! A-ha!

18:20.733 --> 18:23.000
I've been looking
all over for you.

18:23.002 --> 18:24.635
Come with me to the roof.

18:24.637 --> 18:26.270
I'm gonna play
your song for you.

18:26.272 --> 18:27.472
And I'm not going to take...

18:27.474 --> 18:30.575
(GROANING)
...for an answer!

18:30.577 --> 18:33.478
(GASPS)
Did you hear that?

18:33.480 --> 18:35.079
Holy rabies!

18:35.081 --> 18:36.881
Jett's gonna play my song!

18:36.883 --> 18:40.184
Wait. Except he's not
playing it for me, but her.

18:40.186 --> 18:42.086
Ah! I gotta go!

18:45.491 --> 18:46.491
Huh?
Mavis?

18:46.493 --> 18:49.760
Have you guys seen Jett?
Uh, you mean that Jett?

18:49.762 --> 18:51.662
The one hanging out
with you?

18:51.664 --> 18:52.430
(SYNTHESIZER PLAYING)

18:52.432 --> 18:54.932
WENDY:
How can you be in
two places at once?

18:54.934 --> 18:57.902
It's complicated.
I looked into
the Dark Glass

18:57.904 --> 19:00.171
and now my reflection
has come to life.

19:00.173 --> 19:01.839
The what?
Dark who-what now?

19:01.841 --> 19:04.876
The ancient cursed
vampire mirror?

19:04.878 --> 19:06.577
What? I'm not
allowed to read?

19:06.579 --> 19:10.915
You guys gotta help me
stop her before she
blows it with Jett!

19:10.917 --> 19:11.949
He's gonna play my...

19:11.951 --> 19:14.785
<i>♪ Slug guts in my hair</i>

19:14.787 --> 19:19.323
<i>♪ Oh, slug guts everywhere</i>

19:19.325 --> 19:21.692
<i>♪ And I don't really care</i>

19:21.694 --> 19:23.361
<i>♪ No</i>

19:23.363 --> 19:28.332
<i>♪ Ooh...</i>

19:31.336 --> 19:32.470
Yeah.

19:32.472 --> 19:34.438
(GROANING)

19:34.440 --> 19:35.706
My song!

19:35.708 --> 19:37.909
Hey, Spider Fangs!

19:37.911 --> 19:39.510
(GROANING)

19:39.512 --> 19:42.280
Wait. Spider Fangs?

19:42.282 --> 19:45.483
Heh, hey, hi, Jett.
(LAUGHING NERVOUSLY)

19:45.485 --> 19:46.250
Funny story.

19:46.252 --> 19:49.787
UNCLE GENE: Guess who came
to save the day!

19:49.789 --> 19:52.990
Mavis, quick, get away
from your reflection

19:52.992 --> 19:54.659
before it sees you and...

19:54.661 --> 19:55.726
(GROWLING)

19:55.728 --> 19:59.263
...attacks you,
like it is. Okay.

19:59.265 --> 20:02.667
Ah! Stop it!
Let me go!

20:02.968 --> 20:05.503
(HIGH-PITCHED SCREAMING)

20:09.908 --> 20:12.376
How can you tell
which is which?

20:13.712 --> 20:15.413
(GROANING)

20:15.547 --> 20:16.914
Literally no clue.

20:16.916 --> 20:17.615
Oh, come on!

20:17.617 --> 20:19.717
I, for one,
think having two Mavises

20:19.719 --> 20:22.220
just means twice
the best friend.

20:22.222 --> 20:25.523
Aw, Wendy,
that is so sweet!

20:25.891 --> 20:27.592
(GROANING)

20:27.759 --> 20:29.227
We gotta do something!

20:29.229 --> 20:30.995
Agreed! But it should be
spontaneous

20:30.997 --> 20:32.396
and poorly thought out!

20:32.398 --> 20:34.699
Agreed!
Yeah, yeah!

20:40.639 --> 20:42.006
Ha-ha!

20:42.474 --> 20:45.943
Zombie reflection,
you are going down!

20:45.945 --> 20:47.945
Get them to look
into the mirror!

20:47.947 --> 20:50.147
It's the only way!

20:55.454 --> 20:57.255
Pedro, let her go!

20:57.623 --> 20:58.356
Stop!

20:58.358 --> 21:02.426
She's so indifferent,
it's irresistible!

21:02.428 --> 21:04.428
(SOBBING) Please don't!

21:04.430 --> 21:05.596
UNCLE GENE: No dice, kid.

21:05.598 --> 21:10.201
We've already
got one perfect,
original issue Mavis.

21:10.203 --> 21:12.270
Not interested
in any knockoffs.

21:12.272 --> 21:14.839
All right, enough
with the mushy stuff!

21:14.841 --> 21:18.342
Let's send this thing
back where it belongs!

21:24.416 --> 21:25.850
No!

21:25.852 --> 21:29.186
Undead together forever!

21:29.788 --> 21:32.356
(SINGING NOTE)

21:35.560 --> 21:37.194
And Gene out!

21:37.196 --> 21:40.564
(GENE LAUGHING AND COUGHING)

21:40.566 --> 21:42.133
I guess that's that.

21:42.135 --> 21:44.835
Another teen crush
bites the dust.

21:44.837 --> 21:48.506
At least I got
to hear my song.
That was cool.

21:48.508 --> 21:50.608
Yeah, Mavis,
you know what wasn't cool?

21:50.610 --> 21:53.311
What?
You fallin' apart around Jett.

21:53.313 --> 21:54.478
Kinda pathetic, really.

21:54.480 --> 21:59.150
Oh, come on, like you guys
would be so different.

21:59.152 --> 22:00.318
So different.

22:00.320 --> 22:01.585
Totally!

22:02.554 --> 22:05.389
Hey, this isn't
the squash court.
